d</guid></item><item><title>“一带一路”基金未达目标，中国在东南亚面临500亿美元缺口</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3256925/china-faces-us50-billion-shortfall-southeast-asia-belt-and-road-funds-miss-their-mark?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>根据最近的一项研究，中国承诺为东南亚基础设施建设投入约 500 亿美元，但尚未落实到已完成的项目中，这引发了人们对中国“一带一路”倡议有效性的质疑。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 11:30:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3256925/china-faces-us50-billion-shortfall-southeast-asia-belt-and-road-funds-miss-their-mark?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国呼吁国际货币基金组织进行“重大”改革以反映经济实力，这是亚洲的集体声音</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3256953/china-calls-critical-imf-reforms-mirror-economic-prowess-collective-asian-voice?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国人民银行行长潘功胜周三在博鳌亚洲论坛上表示，包括国际货币基金组织（IMF）在内的现有国际机构需要改革。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 09:57:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3256953/china-calls-critical-imf-reforms-mirror-economic-prowess-collective-asian-voice?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>取消IPO后，阿里巴巴物流部门菜鸟将员工年终奖金翻倍，以提振士气</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3256924/alibabas-logistics-unit-cainiao-double-year-end-bonus-employees-morale-boosting-move-after-scrapped?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>电商物流巨头菜鸟将推出“创业激励计划”，将其截至2025年3月31日的财年分配的奖金池增加一倍。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 09:30:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3256924/alibabas-logistics-unit-cainiao-double-year-end-bonus-employees-morale-boosting-move-after-scrapped?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国谴责巴基斯坦造成六人死亡的自杀式爆炸事件，承诺尽管发生袭击仍将继续推进一带一路项目</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3256926/china-condemns-pakistan-suicide-bombing-killed-6-pledges-continue-belt-and-road-projects-despite?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>北京要求对造成中国资助水电站工程师死